  "message": "test(engine): add FRX React corpus conformance fixtures and traces\n\nNew conformance test data for the FRX compatibility verification system:\n\nFixtures (frx_react_corpus/fixtures/):\n- compat.rsc.server_component_hook_violation.fixture.json: Test case\n  for detecting React Server Component hook usage violations\n- compat.ssr.streaming.suspense_handoff.fixture.json: Test case for\n  SSR streaming Suspense boundary handoff correctness\n\nTraces (frx_react_corpus/traces/):\n- Corresponding execution traces for both fixtures, used by the\n  conformance test runner to verify engine behavior matches\n  expected React framework semantics\n\nAlso adds parser_performance_promotion_gate_v1.json fixture\ndefining baseline performance thresholds for the parser gate.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
